The @Mayans were a violent civilization.
The @Mayans claimed to have seen their gods in the sky.
The @Mayans had their very own bible, However the original is not found the copy still exist!
The @Mayans sacrificed their own people for their gods.
The @Mayans had a ceremonial ball game and it's still a mystery today if the losers or winners get sacrificed since being sacrificed was a honor.
